text: Winterswijk is a municipality and town in the province of Gelderland, the Netherlands. About 29,000 people were living there in 2021. Winterswijk lies in the Achterhoek region and borders Germany. == References == * Plaatsengids.nl Category:Settlements in Gelderland Category:Municipalities of Gelderland Category:Achterhoek
